data.description: Welcome home! Pride of ownership shows throughout this cozy, ONE LEVEL, open concept home. Updated with wood laminate flooring, quartz counter tops with new stainless appliances in kitchen. Updated bathrooms with quartz vanities and anti-fog mirrors. Large primary with en-suite walk-in shower, walk-in closet. Corner lot on cult-de-sac, with fully fenced yard and AC via ductless heat pumps. Close proximity to I-5, neighborhood schools and shopping.
